{"tid":2487192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：已致歉並承諾改過　若連任必宣誓擁護《基本法》","createTime":"2021-04-13T11:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T11:45:23.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f3cfd7dffb2a1c4d566048729fbd084245585626","tid":2487192,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n政府提出有關立法會及區議會等公職的宣誓修訂草案，草案建議明文列明「侮辱國旗」、主張「全民公投」及「全民制憲」均為不擁護《基本法》之行為，可因而被取消就任資格，並將視實際情況，考慮議員於修例前的行為。立法會議員、熱血公民主席鄭松泰，曾於 2016 年被判侮辱國旗及區旗罪成；他今（23日）回應指，已於去年立法會選舉參選時，向選舉主任就侮辱國旗及區旗罪致歉並承諾改過遷善，明言「若有幸當選連任，必在宣誓就職之時再次公開宣示之。」<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/dq-時代-曾被裁定侮辱國旗罪成-鄭松泰-已致歉並承諾改過-若連任必宣誓擁護-基本法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdq-%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0-%E5%B7%B2%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89%E4%B8%A6%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E6%94%B9%E9%81%8E-%E8%8B%A5%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%BF%85%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E6%93%81%E8%AD%B7-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Cukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=f885621b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdq-%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0-%E5%B7%B2%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89%E4%B8%A6%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E6%94%B9%E9%81%8E-%E8%8B%A5%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%BF%85%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E6%93%81%E8%AD%B7-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95%2F&h=8242376f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/dq-時代-曾被裁定侮辱國旗罪成-鄭松泰-已致歉並承諾改過-若連任必宣誓擁護-基本法/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaTyuk2qymDBgaYWTu7MGodTZqdjVYY8bmqto8tUL7hao?filename=0jNoR8P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jNoR8P.jpg&h=ad948d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：若我有幸當選連任，必再次公開宣示繼續擁護《基本法》，愛護國旗和區旗。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2419819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2419819</a>"},{"pid":"59734ce80b1b97d28b700c74a7af178151fd5a1a","tid":2487192,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"想知佢最後點死法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94467d5436fbf9ec50c506d5164801051a94bce4","tid":2487192,"uid":200083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"有撚人投你 柒頭"},{"pid":"e6ca7d54f3d8865f21ce855c7c958068b24319b1","tid":2487192,"uid":22701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"有得入閘屎都食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe3ef829cf4c5372d20daf05cbff4d3b368e2bc","tid":2487192,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"feb5c5fb599449e0b75889ad0260cc9712d0581b","tid":2487192,"uid":302184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94467d5436fbf9ec50c506d5164801051a94bce4","tid":2487192,"uid":200083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"有撚人投你 柒頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:30:36.000Z","msg":"有，總要搵幾條友做下戲子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3105c3cb741da8436d2673752cab7463ef7a155","tid":2487192,"uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"94467d5436fbf9ec50c506d5164801051a94bce4","tid":2487192,"uid":200083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"有撚人投你 柒頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"佢呢d有做忠誠反對派既潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804bc356b9e01379285f399c59fda528eb4c7f30","tid":2487192,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"